{{Quote|I hate the Gunboats. One jumped out of hyperspace right behind me on my last mission. Just about scared the scarns out of me.''"<br />"''Scarns?''"<br />"''Yeah, scarns. You know&hellip;|[[Speedy]] and [[Hamo Blastwell]] discuss [[Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wing/Legends|Assault Gunboats]]|<ref name="X-Wing: The Official Strategy Guide">''[[X-Wing: The Official Strategy Guide]]''</ref>}}
